<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-10-15T15:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-10-15T15:00:00-05:00" n="644" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d644">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">795.00/10–1551: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in France</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Bonsai</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                            </seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-10-15T21:00:00+01:00">October
                                    15, 1951—9 p. m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>2195. <gloss target="#t_FonOff1">FonOff</gloss> today showed us telegram
                            dated September 25 just reed from French ConGen Shanghai, substance of
                            which follows:</p>
                        <p>While Sov hand obvious in move for cease-fire negots Korea, it is <pb facs="1065" n="1049" xml:id="pg_1049"/> believed that Chinese
                            Commies’ own desires have played larger part. Chinese press Shanghai has
                            ill-concealed desire for resumption negots and has even implied concern
                            over breakdown. One of reasons for Chinese Commie attitude has been
                            necessity deferring attack on Formosa and reports indicate considerable
                            work all along coast opposite Formosa in ports and on air fields. As
                            possible indication Chinese Commie expectation negots will be resumed
                            and some agreement reached, econ efforts reported on upsurge Shanghai
                            and Tientsin in anticipation.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Bonsal</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>